                       |BKB-= |CKBTrap Room |BKB=-
               
|MKOThis command will allow you to quickly construct a lethal trap
that can be placed in a room.  Anybody, except Thieves, that 
attempt to leave the room, or pick up the trap will set it off,
causing damage to that person.   Any Thief can remove a trap with 
'disarm trap'.


|CKOGLVL required: |GKB10
|CKOSyntax: |YKOtrap                 |CKOCost: |WKO~35
